{"tid":547275,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"Youtube不如放棄賣廣告，直接挖礦算啦","createTime":"2018-02-01T09:39:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-01T16:22:38.000Z","uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f28b6f66ea12ffb6559c29115ccab2626f08464a","tid":547275,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T09:39:28.000Z","msg":"之前在fb上見到有人提議<br />\n部分網站與其賣廣告，不如<span style=\"color: red;\">在用戶同意下</span>「借用」其電腦資源挖礦賺取收入<br />\n，感覺好像幾有趣。綜合作者及留言，有以下論點：<br />\n<br />\n1. 挖礦比賣廣告或眾籌有效。因為廣告隨著Adblock 盛行，逐漸失效，創作者真正獲得的收益低微，而且廣告插播拖累影片進度，令影片觀看、資源下載不暢順；眾籌的問題在於使用者一般缺乏動機去捐錢（嫌麻煩、free-rider心態etc.），創作者為了吸引人捐錢通常會推出一些donor-only產品（T-shirt etc.），但吸引力不大。挖礦雖然會拖慢電腦速度，但大致上卻不影響電腦上下載影片資源的速度，也就是說不會阻礙影片播放的體驗。<br />\n<br />\n2. 有質疑認為目前挖礦程式往往會拖慢電腦速度/ 加快電池用量，而且可能會導致資訊安全問題<br />\n<br />\n3. 亦有質疑認為比特幣（以及其他虛擬貨幣）價值不太穩定<br />\n<br />\n你地覺得可行嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：本人不熟悉比特幣及資訊安全<br />\n<br />\n參考資料：<br />\n文學少年的房間. II fb貼文<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/V9ap8e\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FV9ap8e&d=6skEbpnF%2FXtZDxY%2F7yju5JUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=3f2282bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/V9ap8e</a>"},{"pid":"c4f6917c2acd80e8a02dc4af31530f2d28a1bf5c","tid":547275,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T09:40:25.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff86c4bca51f03392c8d6f5abdcf34cc29646844","tid":547275,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T09:45:38.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc878128985d0925f80742cba8597f9e9cd12a90","tid":547275,"uid":144,"like":20,"dislike":3,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T09:56:16.000Z","msg":"不如直接捉你老母去做雞好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\"